License
This repository is licensed under the MIT License, meaning you are free to use, modify, and distribute it with proper attribution to Xuan Truong.

Features
Plugin Management: Powered by lazy.nvim for efficient plugin handling.
LSP & DAP: Integrated Language Server Protocol and Debug Adapter Protocol for better development experience.
Code Formatting: Supports stylua, prettier, black, and more.
Custom Keybindings: Optimized mappings for faster workflow.
Performance & Aesthetics: Minimal yet powerful, with a clean and modern UI.
Installation
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/xuantruong1612/nvimlua ~/.config/nvim
Install required dependencies.
Launch Neovim and let lazy.nvim handle the rest.

